attachments.title: Russian spacecraft due to re-enter atmosphere, burn up - CNN.com
attachments.text: An unmanned space cargo ship that spun out of control after launch is due to re-enter the Earth's atmosphere Friday and burn up, Russian state media said.

attachments.title: Crazy Vaclav
attachments.text: Crazy Vaclav is the owner, proprietor, and sales person at Crazy Vaclav's Place of Automobiles. Crazy Vaclav appears to be of Eastern European descent, and speaks with a thick accent. Homer visits his business after he wrecks his car in a blizzard during the episode Mr. Plow. Vaclav eagerly attempts to sell Homer a car which he brags "will get three hundred hectares on a single tank of kerosene."
